---
nav: "index"
path: "./"
title: "CC4ES | Home"
description: "CC4ES is a grassroots, non-profit environmental organization dedicated to cultivating sustainable lifestyle in all walks of life.  CC4ES instills systemic mindset by linking communities through its systemic maps while helping individuals initiate small steps."
---

<div class="index-header-hero">
  <div class="grid-container">
    <h2 class="hero-title">Coalition Center for<br>Environmental<br>Sustainability</h2>
    <h4 class="hero-subtitle">Linking Communities for Resilient Sustainability</h4>
  </div>
</div>

<article class="grid-container">
  <div class="grid-x">
    <div class="text-center cell small-12">
      <h2><strong>A Web-Based Center That Cultivates<br>Sustainable Lifestyle In All Walks Of Life</strong></h2>
      <p>Ever emerging environmental, social and economic challenges necessitate a lifestyle that fosters sustainability. Cultivation of a sustainable lifestyle entails continual learning and diligent practices. Such endeavor resonates with the CC4ES core tenets: comprehensive collaboration for systemic changes, community-based and empowered motivation, and establishing an environment for lifelong learning and practice.</p>
      <p>Aligning with its core tenets, CC4ES WebCenter infrastructure is organized in three components - learn, connect and practice:</p>    
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cell small-12">
     <h2 class="green-section-heading">LEARN</h2>
  </div>  
  <div class="text-center cell small-12">  
     <p>LEARN inventories and achives resourcess on sustainability by each of CC4ES Six Modules for continual learning. Six Modules are listed as below.</p>    
     <% link_to 'how-to-navigate-six-modules', :class => "button" do %>
       <h5>How to Navigate Six Modules</h5>
      <% end %>
  </div>  
  <div class="grid-x grid-padding-x grid-margin-x">
  <% data.site.modules.each do |card| %>
    <div class="grid-card cell small-12 medium-6 large-4">
      <div class="card-content">
        <% if card.module_id && card.module_id >= 0
            label_text = "#{card.label}" + " #{card.module_id}"
          else
            label_text = card.label
          end
         %>
        <div>
          <span class="tool-id-label"><%= label_text %></span>
        </div>
        <h3><%= card.title %></h3>
        <% if card.subtitle %><p><%= card.subtitle %></p><% end %>
      </div>
      <% link_to card.cta_page_key, :class => "button" do %>
        <%= card.cta_text %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  </div>
  <div class="cell small-12">
     <h2 class="green-section-heading">CONNECT</h2>
  </div>
  <div class='text-center cell small-12 medium-6'>
      <p>CONNECT houses a compiled network list of organizations in various sectors relevant to sustainability. This list is dynamically updated, ready for network maps integral in coordinating collaboration for collective shifts in resilient community building. CC4ES would like to attribute to Susan Kortes of Providential Gardener, who created the master list and continually updates the list</p>   
      <% link_to 'connect', :class => "button" do %>
       <h5>To CONNECT</h5>
      <% end %>
  </div>
  <div class='text-center cell small-12 medium-6'>
      <%= image_tag('Connect_home2.jpg', :class => 'highways') %>
      <% end %>    
  </div>            
  <div class="cell small-12">
     <h2 class="green-section-heading">PRACTICE</h2>
  </div>
  <div class='text-center cell small-12 medium-6'>
      <%= image_tag('CC4ES_Practice_home.jpg', :class => 'Practice-diagram') %>
      <% end %>   
  </div>            
  <div class='text-center cell small-12 medium-6'>
      <p>PRACTICE features CC4ES programs, initiatives and on-ground cohorts in practice. Although each program has its own specific focus, all of them share the common thread of being initiated, narrated and empowered by members of the communities these programs tend to.</p>    
      <% link_to 'practice', :class => "button" do %>
       <h5>To PRACTICE</h5>
      <% end %>
  </div>
 </article>
